<div id="dg-safe-picker" style="margin-top:24px; padding:16px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:12px;">
  <h3 style="margin:0 0 8px;">ğŸ›Ÿ ã‚»ãƒ¼ãƒ•ãƒ»ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã‚¢ãƒƒãƒ—ãƒ­ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ï¼ˆæš«å®šUIï¼‰</h3>

  <div style="display:flex; gap:12px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <button id="dg-pickBtn" type="button">ğŸ“ ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«ã‚’é¸æŠ</button>
    <span>é¸æŠä¸­: <strong id="dg-fileName">æœªé¸æŠ</strong></span>
    <input id="dg-fileInput" type="file" style="position:absolute; left:-9999px;" />
  </div>

